## Usage

Include any component in your markdown files:

```liquid
{% raw %}{% include components/button.html text="Click Me" variant="primary" href="/page" %}{% endraw %}

{% raw %}{% include components/alert.html variant="warning" title="Heads Up" body="Important message here." %}{% endraw %}

{% raw %}{% include components/badge.html text="New" variant="success" %}{% endraw %}
```

See the [Components Documentation](/wiki/components) for full API reference.
